ib1nKve3HKZhxrUD2R-HkJ4gWQm3I3prv-xMze96mh52m5jtIoZtw_lrmqIXGeuvHx0rUP9eC3H=
6xZJt80wc0xmjoFbig ) that content businesses that succeed on the Internet d=
o so by credibly offering a guarantee of the ongoing production of content =
you will like. For now that means having an integrated branded offering, li=
ke the New York Times or Stratechery; both models are in stark contrast to =
Artifact, which had no integration into content creation and simply attempt=
ed to skim the best of the open web. It may be the case that there just isn=
=E2=80=99t that much good stuff out there.

